==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Charact
<hw>Char"act</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A distinctive mark; a
character; a letter or sign. <mark>[Obs.]</mark> See
<er>Character</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In all his dressings, <qex>characts</qex>, titles, forms.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Character</ent>⟦br⟧
